{"tid":224294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣州一醫院抽血不換針頭　醫生解釋：扎兩三個而已","createTime":"2017-05-01T02:54:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-04T12:12:07.000Z","uid":53379,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa1d7098556962061b8d0e2a38d1ad3ca1648df8","tid":224294,"uid":53379,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:54:45.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">廣州一醫院抽血不換針頭　醫生解釋：扎兩三個而已</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170430/s00004/79aca935ff958f7b66cfbea067eda4b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170430%2Fs00004%2F79aca935ff958f7b66cfbea067eda4b2.jpg&h=dd3af1b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣東省廣州市一家醫院的醫生為病患抽血時沒有換針頭，醫生還說：「應該沒有什麼，就扎了兩三個而已」。<br />\n<br />\n陳小姐上月11日帶孩子到廣州天河區人民醫院看病，抽血檢查後，她身後的另一名患者的家人無意間聽到兩位醫生對話。女醫生大聲問男醫生：「到底有沒有換針頭？」男醫生卻說，「這個應該沒有什麼，就扎了兩三個而已」。<br />\n<br />\n目前天河區衛生和計劃生育局已經介入調查，院生說，涉事的檢查科男醫生是實習醫生，已經離職，而陳小姐發現已要求重新為孩子抽血，希望未來3年內都能追蹤體檢，並堅持要求院方合理解釋。<br />\n<br />\n（廣東電視台）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170430/s00004/1493563271021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170430%2Fs00004%2F1493563271021&d=Tp8cMPEgSVVC2rtXaxUH2sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=6185fe2e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170430%2Fs00004%2F1493563271021&h=b7f3aa84\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170430/s00004/1493563271021</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 蚹蛤蟈蜻"},{"pid":"1815e72e0425ff165b2bc12bf42165449608e064","tid":224294,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T02:55:46.000Z","msg":".....aids"},{"pid":"a0a63176c955649276ad5fbbae810fe3c705289c","tid":224294,"uid":28131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":